text: Audun Heimdal (born 8 February 1997) is a Norwegian orienteering and ski orienteering competitor. He won a silver medal in the middle distance at the 2019 World Ski Orienteering Championships. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian orienteers Category:Ski-orienteers Category:Universiade silver medalists for Norway Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Norway
